genresAdvancedInfo.name: suomisaundi
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Suomisaundi is a Finnish style of psychedelic trance music that emerged in the early 2000s. The genre is characterized by its use of traditional Finnish folk music elements, such as the kantele (a Finnish zither), combined with electronic beats and effects. Suomisaundi artists often incorporate humor and playfulness into their music, with titles and lyrics that reflect this. The genre has gained a following in Finland and abroad, with festivals and events dedicated to suomisaundi music.
